      <ul>
        <li><strong>Behind-the-scenes content:</strong> Show how you make your product or deliver your service</li>
        <li><strong>Before & after:</strong> Perfect for salons, interior designers, tailors, repair shops</li>
        <li><strong>Customer testimonials:</strong> Record a 15-second video with a happy customer</li>
        <li><strong>Quick tips:</strong> A CA sharing tax tips, a nutritionist sharing diet advice</li>
        <li><strong>Local hooks:</strong> "Best chai in Surat?" or "Here's what Surat brides are choosing in 2026"</li>
