      <h3>Consistency is the Key</h3>
      <p>Posting <strong>3–4 Reels per week</strong> consistently outperforms a single viral post. Use local hashtags like <strong>#Surat #SuratBusiness #SuratFoodie</strong> and tag your location on every post to improve local discoverability.</p>
