      <ul>
        <li><strong>Mobile-first design</strong> — 85%+ of Indian internet users browse on mobile</li>
        <li><strong>Fast loading speed</strong> — Under 3 seconds, especially on 4G networks</li>
        <li><strong>Clear CTA</strong> — "Call Now," "WhatsApp Us," "Book Appointment"</li>
        <li><strong>Local keywords</strong> — "accountant in Surat," "interior designer Athwa"</li>
        <li><strong>Google Maps embed</strong> on your contact page</li>
        <li><strong>Schema markup</strong> — Tells Google your NAP (Name, Address, Phone)</li>
