          <p><strong>No Google My Business listing:</strong> Over 60% of local searches result in a store visit. If you're not on GMB, you're invisible to nearby customers actively looking for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mistake-item">
          <span class="mistake-icon">❌</span>
          <p><strong>Posting inconsistently on social media:</strong> Going quiet for 2–3 weeks kills your reach. Instagram's algorithm punishes inactivity. Even 3 posts a week is better than a burst of 20 followed by silence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mistake-item">
          <span class="mistake-icon">❌</span>
          <p><strong>Running ads without a landing page:</strong> Sending paid traffic to your Instagram page or homepage with no clear CTA wastes your budget. Always send to a dedicated page with one goal.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mistake-item">
          <span class="mistake-icon">❌</span>
          <p><strong>Ignoring reviews:</strong> Not responding to Google reviews — good or bad — tells potential customers you don't care. Always reply within 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mistake-item">
          <span class="mistake-icon">❌</span>
          <p><strong>Expecting overnight results from SEO:</strong> Local SEO India takes 3–6 months of consistent effort to show results. Businesses that quit after 4 weeks never see the compounding payoff.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mistake-item">
          <span class="mistake-icon">❌</span>
          <p><strong>Not tracking anything:</strong> Without Google Analytics or Meta Pixel, you have no idea what's working. You can't improve what you don't measure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

